N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 52.2 - Opportunity to be heard

State Regulations

The Attorney General shall not cancel or suspend the name of any particular
individual or individuals from a ticket distributor registration without giving the registrant an opportunity to be heard. Notes
